      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i spend all day staring at a screen with people i dont even know, then i turn it off and the apartment is just... empty. i feel like if i just stopped logging on, or stopped showing up at all, everything would just keep moving exactly the same way. like i'm not even really part of the world.",
